quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,YOUR HEARTS are taken up with worldly gain
  102,2,from the cradle to the grave
  102,3,No! But you shall learn
  102,4,No! You then shall surely learn
  102,5,No! If you knew the Truth with certainty
  102,6,you would witness Hell
  102,7,you would then witness it with the certainty of your very eyes
  102,8,"Then, on that day, you shall surely be questioned about your bliss"